  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package intentionally embeds a future-dated evidence node (W-CON-03): one ValidationResult carries an evidenceTimestamp strictly later than the UnitOfAssurance signatureTimestamp, simulating evidence that post-dates the signed package.",
